rows.name: Ask Duna about recent developments.

rows.label: tev045401_SEL3021
rows.name: Ask Duna if she has any interesting news.

rows.label: tev045401_MSG0001
rows.name:
You would not know it now, but Prone were once
great in number![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG0002
rows.name: We are known for large families.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG0003
rows.name:
My family wants me to marry. Also my brother,
Nemard. They bother us about it every day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG0004
rows.name:
But who do they expect me to wed?
Must I pick from pathetic males remaining?
I could scrape better husband from boot![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG0005
rows.name:
*sigh* Show me Prone who is gentle, yet still strong
like mandos. THIS Prone I will consider for mate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG0010
rows.name:
In Ganglion captivity, we were worked to bone.
Nearly starved to death.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG0011
rows.name: So when we came here, we gorged ourselves on food.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG0012
rows.name: It is good to fatten up. But I must get back in shape.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG0013
rows.name:
Perhaps I will go on hunt. Work up sweat.
Then charm future mate with toned body.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG1001
rows.name:
We once had many brothers and sisters.
They never got to see your city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG1002
rows.name:
They died during wars with Cavern Clan.
Some quickly. Some tortured. But all dead.
Only me, Liana, and Nemard remain.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG1003
rows.name: Nemard's wedding would have brought joy to them all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG1004
rows.name:
It was hard work to plan wedding.
But that knowledge makes effort worth it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG1009
rows.name: Nemard's wedding went well. This is good. But...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG1010
rows.name: But now I get more pressure to marry![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG1011
rows.name: Grandfather is cruel. He views me as lost cause.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG1012
rows.name:
*sigh* Why does mate as strong as mandos not come
sweep me off feet?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2001
rows.name: Lao betrayed you for Ganglion, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2002
rows.name:
Tree Clan believes in solidarity.
If our kin betrayed us, he would get 5,000 lashes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2003
rows.name: ...If we did not give death first.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2004
rows.name:
But you forgive traitor AND rescue him!
This seems soft.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2009
rows.name:
Now Nemard is married, and Hexuna,
so much younger than me, has child...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2010
rows.name:
I see nothing but pity in everyone's eyes.
They no longer even nag.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2011
rows.name: ...It hurt less when they nagged.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2012
rows.name:
This would change if mate as strong as mandos
came along! Strong Prone who deserves me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2017
rows.name: I have found potential husband in your city![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2018
rows.name: So great! He puts "man" back in "mandos"![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2019
rows.name:
...Who is this? It is your commander!
Man like big, muscular beast![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2020
rows.name:
I saw him chase away simius near city gate with bare
hands. Oooooo...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2021
rows.name:
I have never seen male so dashing and strong.
Do you think he will take me as mate?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2026
rows.name:
Now Nemard is married, and Hexuna,
so much younger than me, has child...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2027
rows.name:
I see nothing but pity in everyone's eyes.
They no longer even nag.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2028
rows.name: ...It hurt less when they nagged.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG2029
rows.name:
When will your mandos-like commander realize he
belongs with me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG3001
rows.name:
I have friend named Thea.
She lost her husband before coming here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG3002
rows.name:
But Thea made her peace.
Commended her husband's soul to beasts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG3003
rows.name: Now she is able to dance again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045401_MSG3004
rows.name:
I admire her strength and courage.
I might not recover from such blow.[ST:wait ]
